# m1_kill_dummy.shot — full M1 happy-path loop.
#
# Player spawns at (~520, 920) on a small platform.
# Mid-map wall column at x=1760-1792, height ~160px above floor.
# Dummy stands at (2400, 984). Pulse Rifle range 2400px, 18 dmg, 110ms cycle.
# Dummy is 150 HP, so ~9 hits to kill.
#
# Verifies: stand → run → fall off platform → continue on floor → jet
# over wall → fire-and-kill → ragdoll. Bursts the death sequence to
# catch the dummy-glitches-on-kill behavior.

window 1280 720
seed   1 1
out    build/shots/kill
aim    900 920

# Idle.
at  20 shot stand_t020

# Run right; we walk off the spawn platform around tick 70-80.
at  30 press right
burst run from 60 to 220 every 20

# Continue across the floor toward the wall column.
burst approach from 240 to 280 every 20

# Jet to clear the 5-tile wall at col 55.
at 290 press jet
burst jet from 295 to 335 every 10
at 335 release jet

# Past the wall — keep running until we're roughly under the dummy's view.
burst past from 350 to 480 every 20

# Stop, aim at the dummy, hold fire long enough to drop it.
at 490 release right
at 490 aim 2400 984
at 500 press fire
burst fire from 510 to 620 every 10
at 620 release fire

# Watch the ragdoll/death state.
burst death from 625 to 740 every 15

at 760 end
